I have read all the books and I believe they have done a great job sticking to them in the movie.  Jennifer Lawrence is really good as the leading lady and the rest of the cast  was well chosen.  I highly recommend reading the books as well as seeing the films because you can put faces with the written characters.  The filming of the games was very well done as well.  Watch and enjoy, good escapism with a solid message that we should all pay attention to because it is not that improbable to be our future.

Love these movies. I don't think movies are ever as good as the books. Books contain much more stories about other characters that just cant be cramped into a 2hr move. And our personal interpretation adds a lot to the characters. They have done a good job in capturing enough of the non action to still relate to the characters. Love the story: a totally unique situation, and it's to show that anyone can emerge as a hero a dire situation.
